docs {
  # Get All Organizations
  
  Returns organizations based on user's role:
  - **super_admin**: All organizations in the system
  - **Regular users**: Only organizations they belong to
  
  ## Authentication Required
  - HTTP-only cookie with access token
  
  ## Response
  Returns an array of organizations with:
  - Organization ID
  - Name and code
  - User's role in each organization
  - Member count
  - Creation date
  
  ## Use Cases
  - Organization switcher dropdown
  - Admin dashboard (super_admin)
  - Multi-tenant user interface
  - Organization management panel
  
  ## Pagination
  Currently returns all organizations. Pagination will be added for large datasets.
}
